title: It's OVER For Democrat Cities
description:
In this video, I discuss a phenomena that I have covered before which is the mass exodus of families, particularly those with small children from major left-wing cities. I explain how this is largely due to the same exact policies Democrats put forward to pander to these families, & how in reality those seemingly family oriented proposals are just feel good virtue signals for their new childless base
